  Add github to remote-id in metadata.xml

  09 May 2015; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org>
  little-plugger-1.1.3-r2.ebuild:
  Use rm -f to avoid issues like bug 540182.

  22 Mar 2015; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org>
  little-plugger-1.1.3-r2.ebuild:
  Add ruby22.

  30 Oct 2014; Manuel Rüger <mrueg@gentoo.org> -little-plugger-1.1.3-r1.ebuild,
  little-plugger-1.1.3-r2.ebuild:
  Drop jruby target. Cleanup old.

  21 May 2014; Manuel Rüger <mrueg@gentoo.org> little-plugger-1.1.3-r1.ebuild,
  little-plugger-1.1.3-r2.ebuild:
  Remove ruby18 target.

*little-plugger-1.1.3-r2 (06 May 2014)

